Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has returned to Marineford \Nwith Rayleigh and Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the real reason behind their actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"With Hopes It Will Reach My \NFriends! Big News Spreading Fast!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the solitary island in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they locked you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't even sleep at night \Nand in order to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...We went east and west and \Nsurvived various hardships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our captain who should be in prison \Nbecame a hero in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain Buggy!\N--We've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've trusted and followed \Nyou and we thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at him, New World! That's our captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't know that you guys \Nhad that much trust in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you give up on Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it will be, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the first mate of the \NBuggy Pirates - Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Mohji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the chief of staff - Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's my buddy - Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what they said \Nin the newspaper was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all infamous criminals \Nwith high bounties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! They're heinous \Nprisoners from Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Alvida, do you wanna see something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's Captain \NJohn's treasure mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing! How did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind doesn't blow east or west!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's blowing right towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Straw Hat, he made trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know? He made \Na raid on the Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle he's alive, let \Nalone doing this sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"'First Son of the Sea' Jimbei and \NDark King Silvers Rayleigh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rayleigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wh-What does Rayleigh-san \Nhave to do with Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... wh... wh... wh... wh... \Nwh... wh... wh... wh... wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what's going on? I can't \Ngrasp this situation at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, his father \Nis the Revolutionary - Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his grandfather is \NGarp. And if that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rayleigh-san could be his uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Carrier Bat brought a \Nmessage from the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! How do they know that I'm here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me that the Navy \Nsent someone to get me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the message is "Be ready for it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't believe this!\N--Don't read it before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at the place of Thousand Sunny -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabaody Archipelago, Grove \N#44 in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools, give us that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Straw Hat Luffy's ship, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Revolutionary Dragon's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can sell it to the Navy for a good price!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're in the same business,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can share the profit \Nif you just give it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that, Flying Fish Riders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that! Give us the ship, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you all. I, good-looking Duval...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't let you fools become popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, take our ally's ship! \NI won't make that popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You screwed up your whole speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I live, I won't let you \Ntouch the Young Master's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather touch a girl... \NOh, I made mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you can't touch it! Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Rose-Some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duval-chin, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm so handsome, \Ngirls won't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Cafe should be the \Nfirst! It's very sophisticated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the most popular place \Non the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the Fish-Man Karate training hall, Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Bones that I'd introduce \Nhim to the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duval-sama! She's not aware of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakky-chin, we can get together \Nagain using the Vivre Card, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we learned that Luffy-chin's \Nalive from today's newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so. It will take a little time but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ray-san met Monkey-chan \Nusing it without any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect this ship until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to do that, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Navy or somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't let anyone take the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duval-sama, we have a \Ncrisis! Here comes Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma?! There aren't any \Nbears on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Warlord - Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! He came to see Ray-san before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on our side, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at Sandy Island - Alabasta \NKingdom in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The capital - Alubarna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We chased them away. The \Ncity is virtually undamaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're tightening our \Nsecurity across the country
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but pirates have become more active around \Nthe world since Whitebeard's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be careful for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish all pirates were like \NLuffy-kun and his crew but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, King, have \Nyou read today's newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama was happy about \NLuffy-kun and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW HOURS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is alive as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just a moment, she became very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as soon as she made that face,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she took the newspaper to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's on Luffy-san's arm? \NNumbers? Marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it some new fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so. Luffy-san wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at some city in some \Ncountry in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, why is he here on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! He can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been 3 weeks since the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just barely escaped death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what are they doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got to be up to something. \NIf not, they're just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, Daz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is wounded and wounds \Nwon't heal that easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smart ass! Are you being sarcastic to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm gonna head back \Nto the sweet old New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The news about Luffy's recent exploits...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has reached each crewmember's hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved your brother's \Nlife - Luffy is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry girls, for the long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, we're used to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make sure that you're resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Snake Princess-sama's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess-sama collapsed from too \Nmuch heart-fluttering a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that they'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll get it if they see the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key is your actions and how \Nuncharacteristic they are of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one guy who looks a bit dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure he'll manage \Nto understand it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will understand you \Nvery well. I have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up in the air above the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I got it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it now! Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the giant bridge in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter, Robin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamabakka Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowin Islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...get off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowin! Bowin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bowin Islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you have to say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go see Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? Have I finally \Nreached the edge of this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only traveled 20 meters'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What's wrong with my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're falling into \Nthe island's trap by eating madly'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time, Usopp'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Island - Weatheria...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they closed the Balloon Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we have nowhere to run since \Nthis Sky Island is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to run! Think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy... Can we \Ngo back to my place for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, can't we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! He's not thinking \Nabout how we feel - how selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young girl! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future Land Baldimore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, what do you think \Nhappened to the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kitton, forget about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that man and about the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a big explosion. \NThere's no way that he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him not to push the \Nself-destruct button repeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tehna Gehna Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time to relax for \Nme in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished eating? I'll take the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. And I thought I \Nasked for the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there is a follow-up \Nstory about my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! You don't even have eyes. \NHow can you read a newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It irks me to hear someone mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up soon! Give it everything you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! The Supernatural Moving Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that what it's all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins of Muggy Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! How long are \Nyou gonna stay asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! How many times \Ndo you wanna get beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking care of you - see it from my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? I brought you today's \Nnewspaper that I got from News Coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an update on your captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you! What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Relax! You better relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you done yet? My hands hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a minute! There should be a catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy doesn't do these kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with Rayleigh - it \Nmust be Rayleigh's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there is a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care - just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Luffy's friends are \Nreceiving his messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirates, who have made \Ntheir way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,begin to fight over who will take \NWhitebeard's place as one of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the battle intensifies, a Navy admiral \Narrives to put down the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pirates Get on the Move! \NAstounding New World!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
